This file describes the directives and concepts tested by this test set.

test set name: fsclose01

directives:

  - close()
  - fcntl()
  - fdatasync()
  - fchdir()
  - fchmod()
  - fchown()
  - fstat()
  - fsync()
  - ftruncate()
  - ioctl()
  - lseek()
  - read()
  - readv()
  - write()
  - writev()

concepts:

  - Ensure the close() return -1 with errno set to EBUSY in case the file
    descriptor is still in use.
